Category - Class in pl.myrecipebasket.model
Object Category represents a category of meals, dishes, food occasions etc., to which a Recipe can be assigned to and by which a Recipe can be described by.

CategoryRepository - Interface in pl.myrecipebasket.repository
Object CategoryRepository provides access to database and ability to perform CRUD operations on Category database table.
CategoryService - Class in pl.myrecipebasket.service
Object CategoryService is a intermediate layer between persistence layer (CategoryRepository) and view layer (HomeController and RecipeController).
CategoryService() - Constructor for class pl.myrecipebasket.service.CategoryService
 
CategoryType - Enum in pl.myrecipebasket.model
Object CategoryType represents a type that is used to describe Category and which distinguish Categories that have been provided in application from those created by User.
Comment - Class in pl.myrecipebasket.model
Object Comment represents a message that can be left by User who wants to share his/hers opinion about particular Recipe with other Users.

CommentController - Class in pl.myrecipebasket.web.controller
Object CommentController is responsible for displaying comment.html page when requested by User, receiving Comment related data provided by User via comment.html form and persist this data in MyRecipeBasket database using appropriate services.

CommentService - Class in pl.myrecipebasket.service
